nodes.title: Instructions
widgets_values:
1. Change Server IP Address to your ComfyUI server IP address.
2. Search and install app "TouchOSC".
3. Import and open "comfyui_osc_control.tosc" control panel.
5. Control IC-Light by using the "IC-Light" tab.
6. Please check "ComfyUI Web Viewer" repo for more details:
   - https://github.com/VrchStudio/comfyui-web-viewer

by Tianzi@vrch.io
